{"tid":1553721,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"每晚 7 點正，全世界鬧鐘自動響播《願榮光歸香港》","createTime":"2019-09-08T16:43:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T15:28:21.000Z","uid":206523,"like":106,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"008add1056b15dd1b05390cff19fb6c4516e6d6a","tid":1553721,"uid":206523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:43:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">相信大家點都知，TVB每晚播新聞前都會播國歌洗腦<br />\n就算個個屌都好，起碼大家都知有呢個規律<br />\n某程度上係因為大家潛意識都知呢個事實</span><br />\n<br />\n我哋都要以眾連登仔之力去建立一個香港新規律：<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">聽 國 歌</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n最簡單又唔消耗上網流量的方法：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">下載首歌落電話＞作為鬧鐘鈴聲＞每晚7pm自動響（最大聲）</span></strong></span><br />\n呢個方法更加唔洗要求大家晚晚都等搭正 7 點，<span style=\"color: blue;\">因為電話會自動幫你做呢件事</span><br />\n<br />\n眾連登仔要做的事，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">就係等呢首歌完完整整咁播曬出嚟</span></span></strong><br />\n如果你肯定自己已背曬，而又識唱，可以一齊唱出嚟<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">唔識唱／唔敢唱，請肅然起敬，表示出尊重，唔好令人覺得玩玩下</span><br />\n<br />\n連光明正大播鬧鐘鈴聲都唔敢的毒撚，最後一招：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">扮聽耳機，但每晚都「插得唔好而意外漏曬音」</span></span></strong><br />\n特別係iphone用家，將你3.5mm插孔輕輕插少少<br />\n國歌會「自然」由喇叭播曬出街，<span style=\"color: blue;\">期間請你扮無事發生，繼續「聽」耳機</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>今日係２０１９年９月９日<br />\n由今晚起，每晚7pm，無論你係邊，<br />\n係坐係屋企／行街／搭巴士／被逼搭黨鐵<br />\n只要一搭正 7 點，大家一齊 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">聽 鬧 鐘 響</span></span>！</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: red;\">前 線 願 意 為 你 擋 子 彈 ， <br />\n你 願 意 每 晚 花 1 分 50 秒 播 國 歌 嗎 ？</span></em><br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fy7yRDOLCy4Y&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2BkYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=65a85d44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y</a><br />\n<br />\n何以　這土地　淚再流<br />\n何以　令眾人　亦憤恨<br />\n昂首　拒默沉　吶喊聲　響透<br />\n盼自由　歸於　這裡<br />\n<br />\n何以　這恐懼　抹不走<br />\n何以　為信念　從沒退後<br />\n何解　血在流　但邁進聲　響透<br />\n建自由　光輝　香港<br />\n<br />\n在晚星墜落　徬徨午夜<br />\n迷霧裡　最遠處吹來號角聲<br />\n捍自由　來齊集這裡　來全力抗對<br />\n勇氣　智慧　也永不滅<br />\n<br />\n黎明來到　要光復　這香港<br />\n同行兒女　為正義　時代革命 <br />\n祈求民主與自由　萬世都 不朽<br />\n我願榮光　歸香港</span></em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光</span>　<span style=\"color: green;\">復</span>　<span style=\"color: blue;\">香</span>　<span style=\"color: orange;\">港</span>，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">時</span>　<span style=\"color: pink;\">代</span>　<span style=\"color: violet;\">革</span>　<span style=\"color: red;\">命</span></strong>"},{"pid":"8e17d44d346ea223642789b3e62bea52ffbc7b0c","tid":1553721,"uid":206523,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:43:44.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔洗怕被藍絲廢老屌，因為只係「聽歌」</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">唔洗驚得一個人做會柒，因為你只係「聽歌」</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">只要每人踏出呢一步，互相團結，無野可以再分化我哋</span></strong>"},{"pid":"1d5d3133f5d74a0f4ca72ab7ee252655a22ceed2","tid":1553721,"uid":206523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:44:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"804295a4c66f97ff66c440984705698884b72aef","tid":1553721,"uid":206523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:44:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4915e842f6413746ac16ecad42f56f0ec119af09","tid":1553721,"uid":146724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:44:21.000Z","msg":"推 同十點大叫一樣原理"},{"pid":"a7e99c7f7da052de1742d1ff34418a2a2c3587bc","tid":1553721,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:44:30.000Z","msg":"有得諗喎"},{"pid":"3aefbe4f0998ea9496df386251e731f2d7ca7991","tid":15537